# 🌱 GreenAgent

> *Not "does it work?" — but "will it hurt us 6 months from now?"*

An AI agent that analyzes every GitLab merge request before merge and predicts its long-term **architectural impact**, **energy consumption growth**, **technical debt trajectory**, and **scalability ceiling** — then posts a scored report directly on the MR thread.

Powered by **Groq** (Llama 3.3 70B) + **GitLab API**.

